        "category": "class",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>In moments of viciousness, your curse can partially infect your prey. Whenever you critically succeed with an unarmed attack from the werecreature archetype, the target must attempt a @Check[fortitude|against:spell-class|showDC:all] save against the higher of your class DC or spell DC, or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} until the beginning of your next turn as their bones elongate and form warps. On a critical failure, the target is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} for one minute as the transformation lingers.</p><hr /><p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is Clumsy 2 until the beginning of your next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is also Clumsy 1 for one minute.</p>"
        },
